/// \mainpage MLIR-AIE
///
/// \section main_intro Introduction
/// Welcome to the MLIR-AIE project: an MLIR-based toolchain for AMD AI Engine
/// devices, and the foundation of the IRON close-to-metal programming interface
/// for Ryzen&trade; AI NPUs.
///
/// This documentation describes the **internal** C++ APIs that make up the
/// MLIR-AIE compiler and runtime libraries. It is a reference for developers
/// working on the toolchain itself, not a usage guide. For tutorials, the
/// programming guide, and examples, please see the
/// [project website](https://xilinx.github.io/mlir-aie/) and the
/// [GitHub repository](https://github.com/Xilinx/mlir-aie).
